\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 CHECK THE ROOM}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 LOOK FOR INFORMATION ON THE SEWAGE SYSTEM}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 LOOK FOR FOOTAGE}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 RETURN TO THE LOBBY }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check the room:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (A series of conductors flitter between server towers. I can use the main surveillance computer to check case records.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Look for footage:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Before speaking with Marshal:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (I don't have any surveillance footage to check through.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 After speaking with Marshal:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Checking the scene before the attack might give me some clues. Let's see what we can find.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (I'm looking at the entrance to City Hall. Next to the street there's a crowd of people standing on the front grass.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Next to the crowd there's a woman with rich green hair, fidgeting.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (She moves closer to the Prince\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s car and her hands disappear in her coat. Then she\u8217\'92s back in the crowd. I can\u8217\'92t pick her out after that.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mission set to: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93return to the area of attack\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ll bet I can find some evidence on that street. That woman did something at the scene. I\u8217\'92m sure of it.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Sewage system:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (I scan through the file. This colony\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s sewage system has been maintained. But what about the system under City Hall?)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 RECORDS OF TOWN HALL FROM 0900 TO 0910}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 "INFORMATION REGARDING THE QUERY HAS BEEN REMOVED FROM THIS STATION#FOR MORE INFORMATION PLEASE SET A LINK WITH#THE MAIN ARCHIVE IN THE CAPITAL.\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Why would someone delete records of an old sewer system?)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
