\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 You\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92re in the Marshal\u8217\'92s office. What do you do?}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 CHECK THE ROOM}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 CHECK THE BOARD}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 CHECK THE NEWS DISPLAY}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 TALK TO MARSHAL TORGUD}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 GO TO THE LOBBY}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check the room:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Marshal\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s office is a tornado of papers. Looking closer, there\u8217\'92s an organizational scheme to everything, as if placed by design. Above his desk is a coil pistol, nicked and scratched but polished to a sheen, no doubt from some days in the field.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check the board:}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Before the attack:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Current tracked crimes are strewn across the board, to be updated.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 After the attack:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (All the current crimes are placed in a folder, with notes on the attack plastered across the board.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check the news display:}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 If Before the attack:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (HEAT WARNING IN EFFECT FOR LOWER KINGDOM. Meteorologists are warning citizens of the Lower Kingdom to expect high temperatures and winds in excess of 60km/h throughout the weekend. This is the latest in a series of intense weather for the Lower Kingdom due to what the government has described as \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93due to a combination of increased material production and }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 If after the attack:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (MOURNING PERIOD ESTABLISHED. A Statewide mourning period of a week has been established by King Vlast this following the tragic attack that took the life of the heir to the Throne, Ygne. While the cause of the attack is still a mystery and investigations are ongoing, the period\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 After Zima has investigated the black market:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (KING PROMISES JUSTICE. King Vlast has released his first official statement since the accident that took Prince Ygne. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Today I write to the people of my kingdom not as a ruler, but a father. Justice will be served to those that did this. For now, it is appropriate to grieve.\u8221\'94)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Talk to Marshal Torgud:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 If Zima is supposed to be somewhere else:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (The Marshal is occupied with work. I should focus on mine.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Normal:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Marshal is sitting at his computer. One hand instinctively adjusting an empty cup of coffee.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 If after the attack & Zima hasn\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92t checked archives (first time):}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Marshal is standing by his desk, massaging his hands. I have to wave to get his attention.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Just! Good to see a capable head on this mess.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I want to know where I can find info on a particular kind of sewage system that may not be functioning anymore hear City Hall.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We keep that kind of pre-structure information in the archives. Feel free to take a look.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 If after the attack & Zima has checked archives (first time):}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (I tell him the files on the sewer have been deleted. His face hardens before he gives out a nervous laugh.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93And I guess whoever did it thought we wouldn\u8217\'92t notice?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Then it\u8217\'92s a good thing I found it in time. You\u8217\'92re stretched thin, asking for help from the Capital\u8230\'85\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s clear from Torgud\u8217\'92s look that he doesn\u8217\'92t want to be in this position anymore than I do. Shouldn\u8217\'92t push it.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What about Outer Rim\u8217\'92s Black Market?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Mm. It\u8217\'92s possible someone there could trade in records. The Market disappeared after a raid a few months ago but they always nest somewhere else. I\u8217\'92ve got intel people trying to figure it out but--\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93--But my way is faster.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 [OBJECTIVE: Interrogate an agent or arrest a thug and ask about the Black Market]}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \}}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 If after the attack & Zima has checked archives but hasn\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92t finished with the Black Market:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Just, how goes the investigation?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I haven\u8217\'92t finished with the Black Market. But I do have some questions.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \}}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 After Zima has investigated the Black Market:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Marshal is speaking to a corporal and dismisses him once he notices me. I slide the disc across his desk.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Get in touch with central and let them know what\u8217\'92s going on. Run a background check on anyone entering or leaving the colony.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m going to the sewers to see who answers for this. If you don\u8217\'92t hear from me by stardown then tell the King what we\u8217\'92ve found here.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Understood.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re a good man, Marshall. Don\u8217\'92t let me down.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (He looks as if he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s about to say something, but instead puffs out his chest and salutes. I smile instead. Don\u8217\'92t want to make too much of an impression on him.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ZIMA RETURNS TO LOBBY}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (I think my time in the colony is up. If there is anything that needs to be done around here then I should end it now.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ASK ABOUT THE INVESTIGATION:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ASK ABOUT POSSIBLE SUSPECTS}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ASK ABOUT THE TIMELINE OF EVENTS}
