\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 SAY GOODBYE}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Ask about the investigation:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What leads do you have on the attack?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Our first lead is a mechanic who worked on the Prince\u8217\'92s car before he arrived on the colony.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The other being a suspicious woman we picked up on our cameras. You can view the footage in the Archive.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Ask about possible suspects:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Do we have any suspects in custody?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No one, but I suppose there was an old woman that claimed she saw someone suspicious. It didn\u8217\'92t lead to anything.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Marshal. We can\u8217\'92t afford to overlook anything in this case. Give me her address.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But Just, she\u8217\'92s probably only senile. Heck, she probably just wanted to be on the news...\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (I put my hands around the sides of his desk. Torgud is neither as smart or brave as he looks and he looks like neither.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Don\u8217\'92t waste my time Marshal.\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Okay! I\u8217\'92ll send you her address.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (I can now travel to see the old woman.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Ask about the timeline of events:}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What about the timetable of the attack?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yes, I\u8217\'92ll send it to you after we\u8217\'92re done talking.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Ask about gang activity:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Aside from clearing the murder, I'm here to reassure the colonies that the King is watching over them. What else can I help with?"}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Trouble never ends for people on this colony. One of the larger gangs, the Nesti, has been rapidly growing and doing larger crimes. You\u8217\'92re free to help find out why.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ll add it to my list.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Ask about Outer Rim:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What is life like on the colonies? I haven\u8217\'92t left the capital in years.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yes, you were with the Core, weren\u8217\'92t you? I\u8217\'92ve heard stories--\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m not here to listen about my past.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Right. Things here have been different. Worse, really. The expansion set in the prior decades has reached us in the wrong way."}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marshal: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Too much growth and not enough control. It was a matter of time before something on this level happened. The Prince\u8217\'92s visit was supposed to signal a change, but I guess some people didn\u8217\'92t see it that way.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \}}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Go to Zima\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92s office:}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 CHECK THE ROOM}
