\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 GO TO THE LOBBY}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92m in my office. What should I do?}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check the Room:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Storage crates block out the windows and cover most of the walls. One of them is leaking packing peanuts onto the floor. I remember the moving crew leaving in a hurry. Could be a few more days until I get this place to myself.)}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 [after chapter 2]}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Despite everything that\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s happened, this room is still the same. I should get a calendar, or something to make it more homely.) }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check the Records:}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 CHECK THE INVESTIGATION FILES}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 READ NEW MESSAGES}
